Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official announcement, Binance will adjust the mortgage rate of some assets in the unified account at 14:00 (Eastern Time) on March 14, 2025. This update will be completed in about an hour. Specifically: 
CELO mortgage rate will be reduced from 80% to 70%; 
IOTX mortgage rate will be reduced from 80% to 70%; 
LRC mortgage rate will be reduced from 80% to 65%; 
ALICE mortgage rate will be reduced from 80% to 65%; 
AUDIO mortgage rate will be reduced from 70% to 55%; 
ICX mortgage rate will be reduced from 70% to 55%.

Odaily Planet Daily News According to Spot On Chain monitoring, a whale deposited 3.92 million USDC to HyperLiquid in the past 17 hours to buy more HYPE and open a long position.
Currently, the whale holds 241,876 HYPE (about 3.53 million US dollars) with a floating loss of about 1.47 million US dollars;
At the same time, it holds a long position of 320,333 HYPE at a price of 14.46 US dollars (3x leverage);
There are also 5080 HYPEs with limit orders set between 14.05 US dollars and 14.15 US dollars.
